{"tid":1199886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"War Game裝備分享","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:49:06.000Z","uid":15716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"724aa30f80c9202353d3010683d8be7a80d48d6e","tid":1199886,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"打war game當然唔少得裝備啦，到底點先可以同到裝備先進既對手抗衡呢？<br />\n<br />\n1.面具<br />\n根據心理學，戴上面具既人會有更高既自信心同勇氣。同時因爲面具外型古怪，會令對方產生唔自在既感覺。面具亦令對方難以分辨，起到干擾既效果。<br />\n<br />\n2.戰鼓<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，鼓係古代戰爭已經證明到佢既效果。戰鼓既存在可以激起己方既士氣，同時可以透過鼓聲既節奏控制前進既速度。大家可能心諗war game點拎個鼓岀黎，其實連登仔新年至愛既嘉頓雜餅就係一個好好既鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲餅乾又可以俾你打緊war game既時候補充體力。<br />\n<br />\n3.噴漆<br />\n噴漆既作用並唔係為左扣對方血，而係令對方既裝備無法繼續使用。如果對方既防具例如盾同頭盔都係透明，只要好似玩splatoon咁噴到對方既裝備其實佢地既裝備已經作廢無得再繼續用。<br />\n<br />\n4.電筒<br />\n對手既防具係透明絕對係有利有弊，其中一個弊處就係無法阻擋光線照射。當對手未收到leader指示既時候佢地只可以正面企係度stand by，用電筒照射絕對係一個好方法。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家交流一下打war game既心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0100412acc49189d71bbd95290a4d36a5d5d7323","tid":1199886,"uid":110110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"拎還拎 千祈唔好拎啲玩具槍出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇撚用 只會比藉口對家開槍 害死自己友"},{"pid":"fa52f4d63245f8b7a05926f1736c044cc6c9d72b","tid":1199886,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0100412acc49189d71bbd95290a4d36a5d5d7323","tid":1199886,"uid":110110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"拎還拎 千祈唔好拎啲玩具槍出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇撚用 只會比藉口對家開槍 害死自己友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"攞水槍入滿顔料好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b009e851fa1c048dad8dd7348efe1c28f375e6c","tid":1199886,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39545b5b9bd1925a817a4935c82774982386ee63","tid":1199886,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"每人拎一罐嘉頓雜餅去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係就係難食左啲<br />\n但每人一個罐製造到既聲效可以好澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b64eab7166eac51969e41d992cd59ca32fa6635","tid":1199886,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HmfuLA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HmfuLA.png&h=5fd4bc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論係當容器定防具甚至樂器都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}